{"tid":897952,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係入左U就要做part time？","createTime":"2018-11-11T10:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T03:01:02.000Z","uid":218705,"like":1938,"dislike":236,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dc68cc97ab66c093cf20c5a645204c8a4b1637","tid":897952,"uid":218705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"我身邊好多朋友都去番part time揾錢，一齊傾計個時就話我廢，用屋企錢，跟住開始就有少少排擠我 ......<br />\n但係我媽媽話我總細，以後大把時間要捱，叫我依家多d玩同專注讀書先，唔好去番工<br />\n<br />\n到底係唔係要去番下工呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=唔番工，有得玩總唔玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=去番工，用老母錢正仆街<br />\n<br />\n利申dse完左之後個段假期係有番過工，之後開sem先冇做"},{"pid":"bfd13f6c62cf8a9cb1a3da551fd6b0b3234b7a98","tid":897952,"uid":134695,"like":453,"dislike":9,"score":444,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"仲係學生 理所當然要屋企錢幫手<br />\n不過可以嘅就自己返下parttime<br />\n當幫補下又好 起碼自己都多啲錢洗"},{"pid":"df427306e14bd7e397f43ff155303e57a18f1de0","tid":897952,"uid":82450,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"做ptbf"},{"pid":"3d2d09225335b44111c8ce423fafc36dda725160","tid":897952,"uid":201604,"like":370,"dislike":3,"score":367,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"on9 有時間仲唔揸daddy架跑車溝女咩<br />\n係啲窮撚唔抵得先叫你返工做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edcc25c4aaf97d817dc156c6f284f1ac0f92782","tid":897952,"uid":1524,"like":351,"dislike":4,"score":347,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"過來人比少少建議你<br />\n<br />\n其實大學就未必需要日日都有堂上，除非你自己reg到full晒爆credit。咁如果冇乜堂上，你又唔會日日都溫書咁勤力，咪要搵D part time返下。不過搵都要搵D輕鬆嘅，等你可以以學業為主，隨時走人唔做都得，咁可以睇下你D朋友有冇介紹啦。再者就係，人生流流長，大把日子要返工，讀書返果D唔需要太辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇你屋企應該唔係等你開飯果隻。隨心搵D 輕鬆工啦。"},{"pid":"7e7f23b206c888817a28a9e381886de909759aff","tid":897952,"uid":105863,"like":381,"dislike":13,"score":368,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"Grad左既答你<br />\n出黎返下工個人會醒目d早熟d<br />\n對你將來做長工會有幫助<br />\n做野更易上手，待人接物更得心應手"},{"pid":"32824e2ccecb4d74dd0710122efbefee005a26c0","tid":897952,"uid":181527,"like":143,"dislike":3,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"如果屋企唔係太大壓力 <br />\n都係讀完書先出黎做野啦<br />\n打後做廿幾三十年 你驚死無得做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef05b278f9f77912c51ad7d184a9f789234e07","tid":897952,"uid":47905,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"有得玩就玩<br />\n出黎做野之後你想玩都無得玩<br />\n日日返工放工訓覺<br />\n一年頂多請一兩次連假去旅行<br />\n去完一星期又要連續返工唔知幾多個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要打後廿幾三十年都係咁<br />\n到時無工返又擔心 你想裸辭玩都難<br />\n<br />\n有得玩既時間真係好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0576e68bc867504481e8d2deba46e78357707f1c","tid":897952,"uid":12152,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"依D朋友唔要都擺"},{"pid":"25b2ca358e01c32601960bcad18e4521fe612e95","tid":897952,"uid":33721,"like":14,"dislike":22,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"7e7f23b206c888817a28a9e381886de909759aff","tid":897952,"uid":105863,"like":381,"dislike":13,"score":368,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"Grad左既答你<br />\n出黎返下工個人會醒目d早熟d<br />\n對你將來做長工會有幫助<br />\n做野更易上手，待人接物更得心應手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907f2c6bea0dd435501e18895d62f9e092260d82","tid":897952,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"等錢駛先翻"},{"pid":"f68cac6c6869e694712a4875e69c21836234b0f6","tid":897952,"uid":135957,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"203a06a5876342035fe04bcba1c26040794b3437","tid":897952,"uid":30445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"屋企唔等你d開飯或冇錢交學費嘅話，得閒識多d fd好過啦，最好唔同國籍又可以當學下外語。返part time可以搵得幾多，反正畢業有60年比你返工。但校園時光就冇咁長了。"},{"pid":"cd0e6d46c2da8b650451dd3ed6c254bbf9ed98e6","tid":897952,"uid":128325,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"仲呀<br />\n總你老母"},{"pid":"b42188f2108a8277871575bb1333585172a6bd80","tid":897952,"uid":71712,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"唔好為左搵錢而返工<br />\n係為左開心而返工 , 返工唔係淨係搵錢 可以識下朋友<br />\n個人覺得返過工既人待人接物係會比無返過工好"},{"pid":"53696e60da34d260eb58e5e604ebd983df074c0d","tid":897952,"uid":209773,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"有咩工推介，除左補習，唔想害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4948588c4c53ff5a23855fed30bcfe815afad28","tid":897952,"uid":105863,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"25b2ca358e01c32601960bcad18e4521fe612e95","tid":897952,"uid":33721,"like":14,"dislike":22,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"7e7f23b206c888817a28a9e381886de909759aff","tid":897952,"uid":105863,"like":381,"dislike":13,"score":368,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"Grad左既答你<br />\n出黎返下工個人會醒目d早熟d<br />\n對你將來做長工會有幫助<br />\n做野更易上手，待人接物更得心應手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"00後未返過工？<br />\n派粒膠就走左去<br />\n我就係柒過先俾返d意見<br />\n我又冇講過要pack晒個schedule黎返工"},{"pid":"2884d7538f04184aeb6226b69c583aff8727950b","tid":897952,"uid":35348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"53696e60da34d260eb58e5e604ebd983df074c0d","tid":897952,"uid":209773,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"有咩工推介，除左補習，唔想害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"零售囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa