br />\n家底okay 既<br />\n甚至grad左 去返個零兩個月trip, 去下歐洲澳洲, 去返幾個旅程先返黎現實搵工 整cv 都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n個ex屋企人同親人係我grad緊都講過<br />\n咪咁快搵工呀 有咩想做 呢半年好做<br />\n過左就冇得返轉頭 心態完全變哂架喇<br />\n其實真係好真"},{"pid":"97c338c70cf07e64f88dad11ccc723c3a66ee7f0","tid":897952,"uid":201643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都係咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話希望我可以享受多啲無憂無慮嘅日子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4168381bd6af5b019aad8413fd65605835dfc351","tid":897952,"uid":159495,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T20:46:29.000Z","msg":"唔好聽d on9 講 <br />\n<br />\n你屋企有錢緊係唔好做part time <br />\n如果你係想上進，花多d時間係exchange 同recruiting, 暑假做份好d㗎intern <br />\n<br />\n你part time 多數未又係補習果d，根本學唔到d咩野。<br />\n<br />\n屋企有條件就要用，唔好為左怕俾人地請而去做d on9 part time"},{"pid":"8b9e257fa4632fdb07590fd97f8f4cdbadc97f7c","tid":897952,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T20:55:11.000Z","msg":"窮撚朋友絕交啦"},{"pid":"a6308eced1149dcdd1bf12e0fecf2b268709a756","tid":897952,"uid":29218,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"點解要做大家都做嘅嘢<br />\n過倒模嘅人生"},{"pid":"c06b409fe5df0d7ed085c629778866b9843115de","tid":897952,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd3c27131f91e4fcd3a65b9bbf7d45ddf2a4861","tid":897952,"uid":72794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"撇開錢嚟講<br />\n其實大學可以嘗試翻下唔同工種<br />\n好多嘢畢咗業都唔會接觸到<br />\n其實都幾好玩嘅<br />\n咪當早少少體驗下做嘢嘅感覺<br />\n又無壓力"},{"pid":"987e950f1541b709947ed2e6b1dfd076c1e40fae","tid":897952,"uid":15011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"呢啲根本係睇你屋企環境<br />\n遲下仲有幾十年你返啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":